Hideki.

119
00:08:01,333 --> 00:08:03,266
What am I doing;
am I out of my mind?

120
00:08:03,333 --> 00:08:05,033
But Chi is so
innocent and honest.

121
00:08:05,100 --> 00:08:06,400
What am I supposed to do?

122
00:08:06,466 --> 00:08:08,133
She looked like she
felt so badly, and...

