I admit that Chi is really cute.

137
00:08:51,133 --> 00:08:54,366
When I look at her,
my heart races,

138
00:08:54,433 --> 00:08:56,233
and I can't help smiling.

139
00:08:57,266 --> 00:09:00,200
But, she's not human.

