that series, aren't you?

197
00:13:22,800 --> 00:13:24,133
Uh, yeah.

198
00:13:24,200 --> 00:13:25,733
Yeah, you were in a while ago

199
00:13:25,800 --> 00:13:27,066
with that little
long-haired Persocom.

200
